The Verification Badge (blue tick) is Meta's official mark of authenticity for Facebook Pages and Instagram accounts. One small icon, a big shift in how audiences perceive you.

### What the blue tick does for you

1. **Brand authority**, you instantly look official and established.
2. **Higher customer confidence**, people trust verified accounts.
3. **Improved organic reach**, verified accounts often surface more.
4. **Stronger ad performance**, trust converts into clicks and sales.

### Two ways to get verified

| Option | What you get | From |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Verification service** | Blue badge added to your own Page or account | $600 |
| **Verified Page (ready-made)** | An aged 10K Page that already carries the blue badge | $600 |

